---
// Footer .ey-footer - reconstrução fiel
---

<footer id="footer-contato" class="ey-footer" role="contentinfo" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/WPFooter">
  <div class="ey-footer__container">

    <div class="ey-footer__top">

      <!-- Brand -->
      <div class="ey-footer__brand">
        <a href="/" class="ey-footer__logo" aria-label="Ir para página inicial">
          <picture>
            <source srcset="/images/logo-branco.webp" type="image/webp" />
            <img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="/images/logo-branco-optimized.png" alt="Logo Essência do Yoga" width="48" height="48" />
          </picture>
          <span class="ey-footer__logo-name">Essência do Yoga</span>
        </a>
        <p class="ey-footer__tagline">
          Um espaço onde corpo e alma se encontram. Praticar yoga no Essência é respirar paz, fortalecer o corpo e acalmar a mente.
        </p>
        <div class="ey-footer__social">
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/essencia_do_yoga/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Instagram do Essência do Yoga">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"/><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"/><line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#contato" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="WhatsApp do Essência do Yoga">
